{"tid":1491544,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲唔支持我地係因為佢地睇唔到我地offer到一個點嘅將來比佢地","createTime":"2019-08-20T12:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T04:02:50.000Z","uid":76712,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"90265835682abaacfb86696eff26f6706f56fa26","tid":1491544,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"身邊D藍絲屋企人之所以成日話大家搞亂香港<br />\n係因為佢地睇唔到我地offer到點樣嘅alternative將來比佢地<br />\n覺得我地欖炒之後就會啪啪屎忽等移民/申請做難民<br />\n但我相信我地大部分人唔係咁諗<br />\n我地好愛香港<br />\n好想香港好<br />\n好想保護香港優良嘅制度，語言，文化，價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正因為咁，我覺得大家係往後嘅文宣方面，除左繼續present比人睇，反送中運動失敗之後嘅香港會幾咁唔好之外<br />\n我地都要bring them vision<br />\n話比佢地聽，香港由我地帶領落去只會更加進步，更加美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e973f93dac60c11a8097317ec2513223a66632a8","tid":1491544,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a64445c6d8498e1bb471d46752b5523a5778cc0","tid":1491544,"uid":33471,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"錯 係睇到之後自己係乜下場"},{"pid":"c31c0c95b4a251a6407b3259d5198fc7c9183b3b","tid":1491544,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b002f7b87bf6752d8aa16bd2df46ac4c2fd8ee2","tid":1491544,"uid":207710,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4a64445c6d8498e1bb471d46752b5523a5778cc0","tid":1491544,"uid":33471,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"錯 係睇到之後自己係乜下場"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"恐懼宣傳要溝啲希望宣傳<br />\n咁先有個對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9090f76